{"tid":429563,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女友就黎生日，唔知點安排好。","createTime":"2017-10-09T04:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T12:27:22.000Z","uid":148125,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"07b8e47511cf0e351feb18700391be1af5ba4e2d","tid":429563,"uid":148125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T04:35:44.000Z","msg":"Plan A：<br />\n<br />\n上午：<br />\n睇早場戲<br />\n中午：<br />\n食lunch<br />\n行香港動植物公園<br />\n下午及夜晚：<br />\nSKY100 睇日落，影相<br />\nCafe 103 食夜景晚餐<br />\n<br />\nPlan B：<br />\n<br />\n上午：<br />\n坐纜車上昂平，行下市集，享受大自然<br />\n中午&amp;下午：<br />\n去大澳掃街，睇白海豚，上虎山睇日落<br />\n夜晚：<br />\n出返市區食晚飯（未諗到去邊，由大嶼山出黎真係好遠。）<br />\n<br />\n今年同女友第一年過生日，所以希望好好睇睇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 海洋公園今年我生日佢已經帶左我去，所以佢生日唔打算去返（雖然果次玩唔夠喉）。迪迪尼佢就最唔鐘意既。所以我都唔知帶會去邊到玩好了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"928a5a9bf2943eec95b05a3a4b1ba9f0e40e8bed","tid":429563,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T04:42:00.000Z","msg":"啊，夕陽多浪漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32cd303ed6e7cd95f6280ed006dca126e8ae3695","tid":429563,"uid":137946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T04:47:52.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"4491a7f57df101a419e7774aa5b4310df289d06c","tid":429563,"uid":29198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T04:49:03.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"feb73ed021540daa871960363068310da6ecdcb7","tid":429563,"uid":10084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:22:05.000Z","msg":"A"},{"pid":"556fc62c78bc0fe8b4bf4893d9f54de851875422","tid":429563,"uid":479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:25:23.000Z","msg":"B會好攰<br />\nA OK但中午可以搵下其他野做<br />\n行公園好悶<br />\n玩下密室逃脫or其他野會好D"},{"p